</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="71C6DDC860D03EA78CDDAB90FBDCF49C" pageId="106" pageNumber="107" type="notes">
<paragraph id="A0D1D2E79F43E2ABDA37A8C269D87D48" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AF0D89CC2F785BE0E262A849640B1AB5" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">A remarkable species with flowers clustered at the apex of a very long peduncle. The stigmas are short and stout and commonly 3 in number.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
